Ro,

I really want you too know that I am your biggest fan, I love you so much, LIKE SO SO MUCH! You’re amazing, beautiful, smart, and funny. We have a lot in common, you love baking, I love baking, your birthday is on June 8, so is mine, and so on. Your trying to hide your sadness, but I know how you feel, you don’t have to keep it inside, you have great friends, like Justine, and Mo. I want you too know that it is amazing to be watching you everyday, and commenting on your hilarious videos. I love you, and I feel as if I knew you when I’m watching your videos, and I wish I did know you, but watching your videos makes it close enough. Your not afraid to be the real Ro, from when you guessed that a Carl’s Jr. Cheeseburger was a Jack and the box cheeseburger with Mo, in the Burger challenge, to when you had to eat a spoonful of oysters in the tin can challenge. That’s what I love about you, Ro.

Love,
Your Biggest Fan
